{
  "stem": "27340.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it gave me an association, and I became very, very keenly interested in this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I finally finished my apprenticeship after the war and moved to London to take on a job as a junior draftsman in a design-- in an engineering design office, I was approached by the Habonim people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would I, perhaps, start a movement or a group of-- of similarly minded people in South London?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish population in South London was rather scattered over a very wide area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not as concentrated as it was in many other areas such as Golders Green, perhaps, or Hampstead or perhaps even Edgware-Stanmore as it is today.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I set that task, and within a year we had a number of groups of various age groups going there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that in itself was a wonderful challenge, a terrific experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was through the youth movement that I was called upon to fulfill a very specific task for the sake of Palestine, as it was then called.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, my paramilitary duties-- they were rather odd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While I was apprenticed and-- I mentioned to you I was always interested in a certain amount of this military discipline and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a war going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I joined the Air Training Corps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was an organization to train the young men between the ages of 16 and 18 in some pre-service entry activities.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The idea was to join the Royal Air Force, and I was fortunate enough to be classified or accepted into the group that, in fact, was destined for air crew people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Flying seemed to be something that fascinated me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was very happy there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
